      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is a driver-focused example featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus for optimized torque delivery. The G96 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw gear selection, complemented by a chassis that retains its factory-specified torsional rigidity. Significant mechanical updates include a ceramic IMS bearing retrofit, a fresh Rear Main Seal (RMS), and a recently replaced clutch assembly. The ventilated rotors and four-piston monobloc calipers offer consistent thermal management and firm pedal feel. While the exterior displays minor road-going patina, the powertrain and suspension geometry remain dialed-in for high-performance applications.",
